e cards are divided by the gear size in the reverse side. The small is as the one cost for taking. The medium is as the two costs. The big is as the three costs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;20x Cursed chip&amp;#10;10x Scroll cards *For the variant.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
